4Geeks Academy offers a AI Machine Learning Engineer course that can kickstart a career in data science. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge and promises job placement after completion. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms such as Decision Trees. The curriculum includes real-life case studies and emphasizes the use of industry-standard tools. The course runs for 16 weeks with 3 classes per week, and class sizes are limited to 12 students. The certificates are recognized by multiple organizations. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop